k White/Getty Images for iHeartRadio" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nicki-minaj-Derek-White-Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nicki-minaj-Derek-White-Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nicki-minaj-Derek-White-Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nicki-minaj-Derek-White-Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nicki-minaj-Derek-White-Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/nicki-minaj-Derek-White-Getty-Images-for-iHeartRadio-@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/nicki-minaj">妮琪·米娜 (Nicki Minaj)</a>凭借第五张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nicki-minaj-pink-friday-2-review-tracklist-lyrics-3555287">《Pink Friday 2》</a>登上公告牌 200 强榜首，创造了历史。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nicki-minaj-pink-friday-2-review-tracklist-lyrics-3555287">妮琪·米娜 (Nicki Minaj) – 《粉红星期五 2》评论：重磅续集不负众望</a></li></ul><p>本月早些时候，米娜发布了她期待已久的专辑，赢得了广泛好评和网上歇斯底里。 《Pink Friday 2》拥有<a href="/artists/lil-uzi-vert">Lil Uzi Vert</a> 、 <a href="/artists/j-cole">J. Cole</a> 、 <a href="/artists/drake">Drake</a> 、 <a href="/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a>等流行音乐和说唱巨星的精彩表演。</p><p> 12 月 16 日，《Pink Friday 2》首次亮相就登上 Billboard 200 排行榜第一名，成为这位皇后区说唱歌手的第四张排名第一的专辑。这使得米娜成为今年第一位登上美国专辑排行榜榜首的女说唱歌手。</p><p>该唱片首周销量超过 228,000 张，这是近十年来女性专辑单周销量最高的纪录。 《Pink Friday 2》也是今年女艺人 R&amp;B/Hip-Hop 专辑中规模最大的首张专辑。她的《Pink Friday 2》黑胶唱片销量达到 25,000 张，这是自 1991 年以电子方式收集销售数据以来女性说唱唱片销量最高的一周。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nicki Minaj - Red Ruby Da Sleeze（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QBGX9QirWaU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p>现在，米娜已经拥有四张排名第一的专辑，成为女性说唱歌手中上榜专辑最多的人，超过了福克西·布朗 ( <a href="/artists/foxy-brown">Foxy Brown</a> ) 保持的三张排行榜冠军的纪录。米娜的其他排名第一的专辑是 2010 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nicki-minaj-11750-321642">《Pink Friday》</a> 、2012 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nicki-minaj-13014-316415">《Pink Friday: Roman Reloaded》</a>和 2014 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nicki-minaj-15862-320261">《The Pinkprint》</a> 。</p><p> 《Pink Friday 2》于 12 月 8 日发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/nicki-minaj-pink-friday-2-review-tracklist-lyrics-3555287"><em>。NME</em>给予这张专辑四颗星</a>，并写道这张专辑“感觉像是 Minaj 所能做的一切的巩固和完善——包括放弃了其他艺术家不会想到的流行文化参考……十三年了在《粉红星期五》之后，妮琪·米娜并没有失去让我们感到惊讶的能力。”</p><p>在发行了 22 首曲目的 LP 后，米娜宣布她将为“Gag City”豪华版“Pink Friday 2”放弃四首新曲目。第一个是与<a href="/artists/50-cent">50 Cent</a>混音的“Beep Beep”。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：粉红星期五 2" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/2bYCNZfxZrTUv1CHXkz2d2?utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，米娜谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-asks-nicki-minaj-to-clear-new-vultures-collaboration-but-she-refuses-3559544">为什么她还没有为期待已久的正式发行的《New Body》（</a>她与<a href="/artists/kanye-west">Kanye West</a>和<a href="/artists/ty-dolla-sign">Ty Dolla Sign</a>合作）清除她的诗句。叶也谈到了这个情况，他说： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-responds-to-nicki-minaj-new-body-3559669">“我支持她的事业，所以我不知道那是什么。”</a></p><p>此外，米娜在 Bravo 脱口秀节目<em>What Happens Live</em>上与安迪·科恩交谈时证实， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-says-her-documentary-series-is-still-coming-3559780">她即将推出的纪录片系列“仍在推出”</a> 。她告诉他，“我不希望这部纪录片在没有音乐的情况下出版，那对我来说毫无意义。”</p><p>此后，她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-announces-pink-friday-2-2024-tour-3557359">宣布了将于 3 月开始的 2024 年世界巡演的细节</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nicki-minaj-makes-chart-history-with-pink-friday-2-number-one-3560337">Nicki Minaj 凭借《Pink Friday 2》创造排行榜历史的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
利佐请求驳回“毫无根据”的骚扰和歧视诉讼https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-requests-to-dismiss-meritless-harassment-and-discrimination-lawsuit-3561059?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lizzo-requests-to-dismiss-meritless-骚扰和歧视诉讼Liberty DunworthTue, 19 Dec 2023 15:07:21 +0000 Music NewsNews..Pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3561059 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莉佐出席 2023 年 11 月 25 日在塞缪尔·戈德温剧院举行的《文艺复兴：碧昂斯电影》全球首映式" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该诉讼是由这位歌手的前造型师今年早些时候提出的</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-requests-to-dismiss-meritless-harassment-and-discrimination-lawsuit-3561059">Lizzo 请求驳回“毫无根据”的骚扰和歧视诉讼的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莉佐出席 2023 年 11 月 25 日在塞缪尔·戈德温剧院举行的《文艺复兴：碧昂斯电影》全球首映式" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，利佐已提出动议，驳回她的前造型师指控她骚扰和歧视的诉讼。</p><p>这些指控是今年早些时候出现的，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-named-in-new-bullying-and-harassment-lawsuit-from-fashion-designer-3502090">利佐服装部门的一名成员对这位流行歌星和她的巡演团队提起诉讼</a>，理由是非法报复性解雇、种族和性骚扰以及充满敌意的工作环境。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/167912/Lizzo-requests-to-dismiss-former-stylist-s-meritless-harassment-and-discrimination-lawsuit" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《音乐新闻》</em></a>报道，利佐的代表律师周五（12 月 15 日）向洛杉矶高等法院提出动议，要求驳回这一“毫无根据且淫秽”的申诉。它还声称，这位“心怀不满”的前员工在“拒绝上班”之前“未能完成分配给她的工作”。</p><p>他们还声称，这位造型师在受雇不到三周后就因在 3 月份 Lizzo 在法国巴黎举行演唱会当天“弃职”而被解雇，并认为该案应该被驳回，因为它是在错误的司法管辖区提起的。因为原告“是纽约居民，曾在欧洲特拉华州的一家公司工作”。</p><p>在回应这位流行歌星试图驳回诉讼时，原告律师罗恩·赞布兰多 (Ron Zambrando) 表示：“这项动议是意料之中的，也是利佐团队试图将责任转嫁到受害者身上的又一次万岁玛丽，就像她对其他三名原告所做的那样。”他们曾以类似的骚扰、残疾歧视和报复性解雇指控起诉她。”</p><p>他继续说道：“利佐和她的律师可以继续努力为她的非法和恶劣行为合理化，但我们仍然致力于为我们的客户寻求正义，并期待着法庭上利佐能够在公共论坛上解释她的行为的那一天。” </p><figure id="attachment_3561062" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3561062" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3561062" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-2023@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Lizzo 出席 2023 年 11 月 10 日在比佛利希尔顿酒店举行的 Femme It Forward Give Her FlowHERS Gala 2023" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-2023@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-2023@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-2023@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-2023@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-2023@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-2023@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3561062" class="wp-caption-text"> Lizzo 于 2023 年 11 月 10 日在比佛利希尔顿酒店出席 Femme It Forward Give Her FlowHERS Gala 2023。图片来源：Robin L Marshall/WireImage/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>这并不是利佐第一次面临前雇员的法律诉讼。早在八月，就有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-sued-by-backup-dancers-for-sexual-harassment-and-creating-hostile-work-environment-3476570">这位歌手的三名前伴舞对她提起诉讼，指控她营造敌对的工作环境并进行性骚扰等指控</a>。</p><p>这些事件据称发生在2021年至2023年之间。作为回应，利佐否认了所有指控——将前舞者提起的诉讼描述为“捏造的悲伤故事”，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-asks-judge-to-dismiss-fabricated-sob-story-against-her-3524240">提出动议要求法院驳回诉讼</a>。</p><p>该动议要求法院根据反SLAPP（反对公众参与的战略诉讼）法规驳回诉讼，该法规有权驳回威胁言论自由的诉讼。</p><p>八月，代表三名舞者的律师声称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lawyers-reviewing-new-complaints-from-more-of-lizzos-former-dancers-3480608">他的公司正在审查至少六项针对这位歌手的新投诉</a>。</p><p>另据报道，1 月，Lizzo 的 14 名舞者因另一起与 2022 年纪录片<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/lizzo-shares-first-trailer-from-her-forthcoming-hbo-documentary-love-lizzo-3347060">《爱，Lizzo》</a></em>镜头相关的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/14-of-lizzos-dancers-received-settlement-for-separate-dispute-months-before-new-harassment-lawsuit-3487569">纠纷获得和解</a>。舞者们声称，他们讨论厌女症、种族主义和体重羞辱的场景是未经授权使用的。利佐的律师评论说，这位歌手与这场纠纷“无关”，并且“对此一无所知”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3561063" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3561063" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3561063" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Lizzo 于 2023 年 7 月 26 日在新西兰奥克兰 Spark Arena 表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/